    <p class="muted">Clean, peaceful, and YES the road is aesthetic — Insta folks love it.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590055536968-fd58cbd3dca2" />
    <h3>Pilikula Nisargadhama</h3>
    <p class="muted">Nature park, lake, boating, zoo — basically picnic paradise.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519681393784-d120267933ba" />
    <h3>Sulthan Battery</h3>
    <p class="muted">A historic watchtower with river views. Also: insanely windy.</p>
  </div>
